<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS, if IPI request to server is sent successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_INVALID_PARAM, if any argument is invalid.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE, if sending IPI request to server fails. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
